    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles its 8,000 RPM redline with absolute composure. The factory suspension geometry remains true, and the braking system provides firm, fade-free modulation. Presented in concours-level condition with impeccable paint depth and a pristine cabin, this is a purist's machine with zero mechanical compromises.",
